  <entry>
    <title>Markdown learning</title>
    <link href="http://lan5th.github.io/2020/09/02/markdown/"/>
    <id>http://lan5th.github.io/2020/09/02/markdown/</id>
    <published>2020-09-02T07:41:47.191Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-03T03:02:02.362Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="ж јејҸ"><a href="#ж јејҸ" class="headerlink" title="ж јејҸ"></a>ж јејҸ</h2><h3 id="д»Јз Ғеқ—"><a href="#д»Јз Ғеқ—" class="headerlink" title="д»Јз Ғеқ—"></a>д»Јз Ғеқ—</h3><p>иЎҢеҶ…ејҸдёӨеӨҙеҠ дёҠеҸҚеј•еҸ·`</p><p>еӨҡиЎҢд»Јз ҒдёҠдёӢиЎҢеҠ дёүйҮҚеҸҚеј•```</p><p>ж®өиҗҪеүҚеҠ еӨ§дәҺеҸ·(еҸҜеҲҶзә§)<br><code>&gt;ж®өиҗҪ1</code> <code>&gt;&gt;ж®өиҗҪ2</code></p><p>дёүз§ҚеҲҶеүІзәҝ<code>***жҲ–---жҲ–___</code></p><p>жҚўиЎҢеҸҜз”Ё<code>&lt;br\&gt;</code></p><h3 id="иЎЁж ј"><a href="#иЎЁж ј" class="headerlink" title="иЎЁж ј"></a>иЎЁж ј</h3><p><strong>ж— еәҸеҲ—иЎЁ</strong> *-+(еҠ еҸ·з©әж ј)<br><code>+ sad</code><br>еӨҡзә§еҲ—иЎЁ(еүҚйқўеҠ tab)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">+ дёҖеұӮ</span><br><span class="line">  + дәҢеұӮ</span><br><span class="line">    + дёүеұӮ</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>жңүеәҸеҲ—иЎЁ</strong>(ж•°еӯ—.з©әж ј)<br><code>1. first</code></p><p><strong>иЎЁж ј</strong><br>еҠ з©әж јдҪҝеҜ№йҪҗпјҲйқһеҝ…иҰҒпјүеҶ’еҸ·и®ҫзҪ®еҜ№е…¶ж–№еҗ‘</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|Tables       |Are          |Cool |</span><br><span class="line">|------       |:----:       |----:|</span><br><span class="line">|col 3 is     |right-aligned|$1600|</span><br><span class="line">|col 2 is     |centered     |$12  |</span><br><span class="line">|zebra stripes|are neat     |$1   |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="еӯ—дҪ“"><a href="#еӯ—дҪ“" class="headerlink" title="еӯ—дҪ“"></a>еӯ—дҪ“</h2><p>е°Ҹж ҮйўҳеүҚеҠ #(space)<br>ж–ңеүҚеҗҺ*<br>зІ—еүҚеҗҺ**<br>зІ—ж–ңеүҚеҗҺ***<br>еҲ йҷӨеӯ—еүҚеҗҺ~~<br>зј©иҝӣ<code>&amp;emsp;</code>пјҲдёҖдёӘдёӯж–Үеӯ—з¬Ұпјү<br>еҚҠдёӘ<code>&amp;ensp;</code><br>еӣӣеҲҶд№ӢдёҖдёӘ<code>&amp;nbsp;</code><br>еұ…дёӯпјҲhtmlж Үзӯҫпјү</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div align&#x3D;center&gt;(еҶ…е®№)</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="й“ҫжҺҘ"><a href="#й“ҫжҺҘ" class="headerlink" title="й“ҫжҺҘ"></a>й“ҫжҺҘ</h2><p><strong>и¶…й“ҫжҺҘ</strong><br><code>[жҳҫзӨәеҗҚз§°](http://www.bilibili.com &quot;жіЁйҮҠеҗҚз§°&quot;)</code><br>зӣҙжҺҘжҳҫзӨә<code>&lt;http://www.bilibili.com&gt;</code><br>еҗҺж–№жіЁйҮҠ<code>[еҗҚз§°1][wangzhi1]</code></p><p><strong>еӣҫзүҮй“ҫжҺҘ</strong><br><code>![еҗҚз§°](..\images\test.png)</code><br>еҗҺж–№жіЁйҮҠ<code>![еҗҚз§°1][image1]</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[wangzhi1]:http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.bilibili.com</span><br><span class="line">[image1]:..\images\test.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p><strong>иҜҰз»ҶиҜӯжі•</strong>пјҡ<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/u014061630/article/details/81359144?biz_id=102&utm_term=markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduweb~default-0-81359144&spm=1018.2118.3001.4187#25-%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97">csdnж•ҷзЁӢ</a></p><p><strong>еҚҡе®ўжҗӯе»әеҸӮиҖғ</strong><br><a href="https://koorye.github.io/2020/07/11/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8GitHub+Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/">kooryeзҡ„еҚҡе®ў</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;ж јејҸ&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#ж јејҸ&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;ж јејҸ&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;ж јејҸ&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&quot;д»Јз Ғеқ—&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#д»Јз Ғеқ—&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;д»Јз Ғеқ—&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;д»Јз Ғеқ—&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
